Revenues from mobile games were $203.3 million for 2015, compared to $66.2 million and $1.7 million, respectively, for 2014 and 2013. Both of the increases in 2015 and 2014 were mainly due to increase in revenues from Changyou’s mobile game TLBB 3D, which was launched in the fourth quarter of 2014.

