Table of Contents
Cost of Others Revenues

Cost of revenues for other services was $80.6 million for 2015, compared to $71.5 million and $55.9 million, respectively, for 2014 and 2013. The year-on-year increase for 2015 was $9.1 million, which was mainly due to $5.7 million in film production costs for “Jian Bing Man” that were recognized concurrently with revenue in the third quarter of 2015. The year-on-year increase for 2014 was $15.5 million, which was mainly due to revenue-sharing payments related to the IVAS business.

